hadiths[65]{hadithnumber,text}:
617,"Main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ke paas aaya , aap Kaabe ke saye mein bethey they aap ne mujhey aata dekha to farmaya : '' Kaba ke Rab ki qism ! qiyamat ke din yehi log khasaray (nuksaan) mein hongey.'' padhi. mainey apney ji mein kaha : shayad koi chiz merey barey mein nazil ki gaee ho. mainey arz kiya : kon log? merey maa baap aap par qurban hon? to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''yehi log jo bahut maal waley hain siwaye un logon ke jo aisa aisa karey, aap ney apney dono haath sey lap bhar kar apney samney aur apney daain aur apney baain taraf ishara kiya, phir farmaya : ''qasam hai us zaat ki jis ke haath mein meri jaan hai, jo bhi aadmi oont aur gaaey chhod kar mara aur usney uski zakat ada nahin ki to qiyamat ke din wo us sey ziyada bhari aur motey ho kar ayengey jitna wo they padhi. aur usey apni khuron sey rondengey, aur apni seengon sey maarengey, jab unka aakhiri janwer bhi guzar chukeyga to phir pehla lota diya jaeyga. yahan tak ke logon ke darmiyan faisla kar diya jaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi isi ke jaisi riwayat hai, 3- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke zakat rok leney waley par lanat ki gaee hai. 4- (ye hadees) Qabisa bin Halab ney apney walid Halab sey riwayat ki hai, isi ke saath Jabir bin Abdullah aur Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 5- Zuhaak bin Muzaahim kehtey hain ke « الأكثرون » sey murad wo log hain jin ke paas das hazar (dirham ya deenar) hon."
618,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum ney apney maal ki zakat ada kar di to jo tumharey zimme fariza tha usey tum ney ada kar diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey dusri aur sanadon sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke aap ney zakat ka zikr kiya, to eik shakhs ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kya merey ooper iskey ilawa bhi kuchh hai? aap ney farmaya : ''nahin siwaye uskey ke tum bator nafl kuchh do.'' (ye hadees aagey aa rahi hai.)"
619,"Hum logon ki khahish hoti thi ke koi aqlmand Erabi (dehati) (dehati) aaye aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey masla puchhey aur hum aap key paas hon padhi. hum aap key paas they ke usi doran aap key paas eik Erabi (dehati) aaya padhi. aur aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ke samney do zaanu ho kar beth gaya. aur puchha : aey Muhammad ! aap ka qaasid hamarey paas aaya aur us ne hamein bataya ke aap kehtey hain ke aap ko Allah ney Rasool bana kar bheja hai (kya ye sahih hai?). Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''haan, ye sahih hai''  usne kaha : qism hai us zaat ki jisney aasman buland kiya, zamin aur pahad nasab kiye. kya Allah ney aap ko Rasool bana kar bheja hai? Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''haan''  usne kaha : aap ka qaasid hum sey kehta hai ke aap farmatey hain : hum par din aur raat mein paanch namaz farz hain (kya aisa hai?), Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''haan''  usney kaha : qism hai us zaat ki, jisney aap ko Rasool banaya hai ! kya aap ko Allah ney is ka hukm diya hai? aap ney farmaya : ''haan''  usne kaha : aap ka qaasid kehta hai ke aap farmatey hain : hum par saal main eik maah ke roze farz hain (kya ye sahih hai?), Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''haan wo (sach keh raha hai)'' Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) ney mazeed kaha : qism hai us zaat ki jisney aap ko Rasool bana kar bheja hai kya Allah ney aap ko is ka hukm diya hai? Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''haan (diya hai '', usney kaha : aap ka qaasid kehta hai ke aap farmatey hain : hum par hamarey maalon mein zakat wajib hai (kya ye sahih hai?), Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''haan (usne sach kaha).'' usney kaha : qism hai us zaat ki, jisney aap ko Rasool bana kar bheja hai, kya Allah ney aap ko is ka hukm diya hai? Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''haan''  (diya hai) usney kaha : aap ka qaasid kehta hai ke aap farmatey hain : hum mein sey har us shakhs par Baitul-Allah ka Haj farz hai jo wahan tak pahunchney ki istataat (taaqat) rakhta ho (kya ye sach hai?), Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''haan  (hajj farz hai)'' usney kaha : qism hai us zaat ki jisney aap ko Rasool bana kar bheja hai, kya Allah ney aap ko is ka hukm diya hai? Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''haan (diya hai) '' to usney kaha : qism hai us zaat ki jisney aap ko haq key sath mab-us (bheja), farmaya : main in mein sey koi chiz nahin chhodunga aur na main is mein kisi chiz ka izafa karunga, phir ye keh kar wo wapis chal diya tab Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''agar Erabi (dehati) ney sach kaha hai to wo jannat mein dakhil hoga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, aur is sanad key ilawa dusri sanadon sey bhi ye hadees Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko suna : wo keh rahey they ke baaz ehle-ilm farmatey hain : is hadees sey ye baat nikalti hai ke shagrid ka ustad ko padh kar sunana ustad sey sun-ney hi ki tarah hai. 3- unhoney daleel is tarah sey di hai ke Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko maloomat pesh ki to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney uski tasdeeq farmaey."
620,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main ney ghodon aur ghulamon ki zakat maaf kar di hai padhi. to ab tum chaandi ki zakat ada karo padhi. , har chaalis dirham par eik dirham , eik sau nawwey dirham mein kuchh nahin hai, jab do-sau dirham ho jaeyn to un mein paanch dirham hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aamash aur abu Awaana , waghaira ney bhi ye hadees ba-tareeq : (abi Is'haaq an Aasim bin Zamra an Ali) riwayat ki hai, aur Sufiyan Sory , Sufiyan bin Uena aur deegar kaee logon ney bhi b-tareeq : (Abi Is'haaq an Al-Haaris an Ali) riwayat ki hai. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is hadees key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : Abu-Is'haq Sabeei sey marvi  (riwayat hui) ye dono hadisein merey nazdik sahih hain, guman hai ke ye Haris aur Aasim dono sey eik sath riwayat ki gaee ho (to Abu-Is'haq ney isey dono sey riwayat kiya ho) 3- is bab mein abu-Bakar Siddiq aur Amr bin Hazam sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
621,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney zakat ki dastawez tehreer karaai, abhi isey Ummaal (governoron) ke paas rawana bhi nahin kar sakey they ke aap ki wafat ho gaee, aur isey aap ney apni talwaar key paas rakh diya padhi. , aap wafat farma gaey to abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) is par amal karte rahey yahan tak ke wo bhi faut ho gaey, un ke baad umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi isi par amal karte rahey, yahan tak ke wo bhi faut ho gaey, is kitab mein tehreer tha : ''paanch oonton mein , eik bakri zakat hai. das mein do bakriyan , pandarah mein teen bakriyan aur bees mein chaar bakriyan hain. pachchees sey ley kar paintees tak main eik saal ki oontni ki zakat hai, jab is sey ziyada ho jaeyn to paintaalees tak mein do saal ki oontni ki zakat hai. aur jab is sey ziyada ho jaeyn to saath tak mein teen saal ki eik oontni ki zakat hai. aur jab is sey ziyada ho jaeyn to picch'hattar tak mein chaar saal ki eik oontni ki zakat hai aur jab is sey ziyada ho jaeyn to nawwey tak mein do saal ki do oonton ki zakat hai. aur jab is sey ziyada ho jaeyn to in mein eik-sau-bees tak teen saal ki do oonton ki zakat hai. jab eik-so-bees sey zayed ho jaeyn to har pachas mein teen saal ki eik oontni aur har chaalis mein do saal ki eik oontni zakat mein deeni hogi. aur bakriyon key silsiley mein is tarah tha : chaalis bakriyon main eik bakri ki zakat hai, eik-so-bees tak, aur jab is sey ziyada ho jaeyn to do-sau tak mein do bakriyon ki zakat hai, aur jab is sey ziyada ho jaeyn to teen-sau tak mein teen bakriyon ki zakat hai. aur jab teen-sau sey ziyada ho jaeyn to phir har sau par eik bakri ki zakat hai. phir is mein kuch nahin yahan tak ke wo chaar-sau ko pahunch jaeyn, aur (zakaat waley) mutafarriq (alag-alag) (maal) ko jama nahin kiya jaeyga padhi. aur jo maal jama ho usey sadqey key khof sey mutafarriq (alag-alag) nahin kiya jaeyga padhi. aur jin mein do sajhi-daar daar hon to wo apney apney hissey ki sharaakat key hisab sey den gey. sadqey mein koi boodha aur aeb daar janwer nahin liya jaeyga.'' Zohri kehtey hain : jab sadqa wasul karney wala aaye to wo bakriyon ko teen hisson mein taqseem karey, pehli tihai behtar qism ki hogi , dusri tihai osat darjey ki aur teesri tihai kharab qism ki hogi, phir sadqa wasul karney wala osat darjey wali bakriyon mein sey ley. Zohri ney gaaey ka zikr nahin kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar ki hadees Hasan hai. 2- Yunus bin Yazeed aur deegar kaee logon ney bhi ye hadees Zohri sey, aur Zohri ney Salim sey riwayat ki hai, aur in logon ney isey marfoo bayan nahin kiya. sirf Sufiyan bin Husain hi ney isey marfooan riwayat kiya hai. 3- aur isi par aam fuqaha ka amal hai. 4- is bab mein abu-Bakar Siddiq Behaz bin Hakeem an Abiy an Muawiya bin Qushairi hai Abu-Zar aur Anas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
622,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tees gaaey main eik saal ka bachhwa, ya eik saal ki bachhiya ki zakat hai aur chaalis gaayon mein do saal ki bachhiya ki zakat hai (daanti yani do daant wali). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdus-Salaam bin Harab ney isi tarah ye hadees Khusaif sey riwayat ki hai, aur Abdus-Salaam bharosemand hain Hafiz hain. 2- Shurek ney bhi ye hadees ba-tareeq : (Khusaif an abi Ubaida an Abdullah) riwayat ki hai. 3- aur Abu-Ubaida bin Abdullah ne apney walid Abdullah sey nahin suna hai. 4- is bab mein Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai."
623,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey Yamen bheja aur hukm diya ke main har tees gaaey par eik saal ka bachhwa ya bachhiya zakat mein lun aur har chaalis par do saal ki bachhiya zakaat mein lun , aur har (zimmi) baligh sey eik Dinar ya uskey barabar muaafiri kapdey bator jiziya lun. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- baaz logon ney ye hadees ba-tareeq : (Sufiyaan, an Aamash , an abi Wayl , an Masrooq) mursalan riwayat ki hai padhi. ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Muaz ko Yamen bheja aur is mein « فأمرني أن آخذ » key bajaey « فأمره أن يأخذ » hai aur ye ziyada sahih hai."
624,Mainey abu-Ubaida bin Abdullah sey puchha : kya wo (apney walid) Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey koi chiz yad rakhtey hain? unhoney kaha : nahin.
625,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yamen (ki taraf apna aamil bana kar) bheja aur un sey farmaya : ''tum ehale kitab ki eik jamaat key paas ja rahey ho, tum unhen dawat dena ke wo is baat ki gawahi den ke Allah key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin aur ye ke main Allah ka Rasool hun, agar wo is ko maan lein to unhen batana ke Allah ney un par raat aur din mein paanch waqt ki namaz farz ki hai, agar wo isey maan lein to unhen batana ke Allah ney un ke maal mein zakat farz ki hai, jo un ke maaldaaron sey li jaeygi aur unkey fuqaraa aur miskinon ko lota di jaeygi, agar wo isey maan lein to tum unkey umda maal leney sey apney aap ko bachaanaa aur mazloom ki bad-dua sey bachna, isliye ke uskey aur Allah ke darmiyan koi parda haael (rukaawat) nahin hota. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Sunabihi (Raziallahu anhu) padhi. sey bhi riwayat hai,"
626,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''paanch oonton padhi. sey kam mein zakat nahin hai, aur paanch auqiya padhi. chaandni sey kam mein zakat nahin hai aur paanch wasq padhi. ghalley sey kam mein zakat nahin hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Abu-Hurera , ibne-Umar , Jabir aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
627,"Abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah ki hadees bayan ki hai jaisey Abdul-Azeez bin Muhammad ki hadees hai jisey unhoney Amr bin Yahya sey riwayat ki hai (jo ooper guzar chuki hai). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- un sey ye riwayat aur bhi kaee turq sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai. 3- ehle-ilm ka amal isi par hai ke paanch wasq sey kam ghalley mein zakat nahin hai. eik wasq saath (60) saa ka hota hai. aur paanch wasq mein teen-sau saa hotey hain. Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka saa saadhey paanch ritl (lag-bhag chaalis taule) ka tha aur ehle-koofa ka saa aath ritl (lag-bhag chaalis taule) ka , paanch auqiya chaandi sey kam mein zakat nahin hai, eik auqiya chaalis dirham ka hota hai. aur paanch auqiya ke do-sau dirham hotey hain. isi tarah sey paanch oont sey kam mein zakat nahin hai. jab pachchees oont ho jaeyn to un main eik saal ki oontni ki zakat hai aur pachchees oont sey kam mein har paanch oont par eik bakri zakat hai."
628,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''musalman par na uskey ghodon mein zakat hai aur na hi uskey ghulamon mein zakat hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 3- aur isi par ehle-ilm ka amal hai ke paaltu ghodon mein jinhen dana chaara baandh kar khilatey hain zakat nahin aur na hi ghulamon mein hai, jabke wo khidmat key liye hon siwaey iske ke wo tijarat key liye hon. aur jab wo tijarat ke liye hon to un ki qeemat mein zakat hogi jab un par saal guzar jaey."
629,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''shehad mein har das mashak par eik mashak zakat hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein abu-Huraira, Abu Sayyara Mutaee aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 2- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees ki sanad mein kalam hai.  Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey is baab mein kuchh ziyada sahih cheezen marvi (riwayat hui) nahin aur isi par aksar ehle-ilm ka amal hai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi isi ke qaail hain. 3- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke shehad mein koi zakat nahin. 4- Sadqa bin Abdullah Hafiz nahin hain. Nafey sey is hadees ko riwayat karney mein Sadqa bin Abdullah ki mukhalifat ki gaee hai."
630,"Mujh sey umr bin Abdul-Azeez ney shehad ki zakat ke barey mein puchha to mainey kaha ke hamarey paas shehad nahin ke hum uski zakat den, lekin hamein Mughira bin Hakeem ney khabar di hai ke shehad mein zakat nahin hai. to umr bin Abdul-Azeez ney kaha : ye insaaf par mabni aur pasandida baat hai. chunanche unhoney logon ko likha ke in sey shehad ki zakat maaf kar di jaey."
631,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisey koi maal hasil ho to is par koi zakat nahin jab tak ke is par uskey Malik key yahan eik saal na guzar jaey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Sraa binteNabhaan Ghanwiya (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
632,"jisey koi maal hasil ho to is par zakat nahin jab tak ke uskey yahaan us maal par eik saal na guzar jaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye (maqoof) hadees Abdur-Rehman bin Zaid bin Aslam ki (marfoo) hadees sey ziyada sahih hai. 2- Ayub , Ubedullah bin umr aur deegar kaee logon ney Nafey sey aur unhoney ibne-Umar sey moqufan (hi) riwayat ki hai. 3- Abdur-Rehman bin Zaid bin Aslam hadees mein zaeef hain, Ahmed bin Hanbal , Ali bin Madeeni aur unkey ilawa deegar muhaddeseen ney in ko zaeef thehraaya hai wo kasrat sey ghaltiyaan kartey hain. 4- Sahaba kiram mein sey kaee logon sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke hasil shuda maal mein zakat nahin hai, jab tak ke is par saal na guzar jaey, Malik bin Anas , Shafai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya isi key qaail hain. 5- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke jab aadmi ke paas pehley sey itna maal ho jis mein zakat wajib ho to hasil shuda maal mein bhi zakat wajib hogi aur agar uskey paas hasil shuda maal key ilawa koi aur maal na ho jis mein zakat wajib hui ho to kamaey huye maal mein bhi koi zakat wajib nahin hogi jab tak ke is par saal na guzar jaey, aur agar isey  (pehley sey nisaab ko pahunchey huye) maal par saal guzarney sey pehley koi kamaya huwa maal mila to wo us maal key sath jis mein zakat wajib ho gaee hai, maale mustfaad ki bhi zakat nikaleyga Sufiyan Sory aur ehle-koofa isi ke qaail hain."
633,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''eik sar zamin par do qibley hona durust nahin padhi. aur na hi musalmanon par jiziya durust hai.''
634,"Qaaboos sey isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas ki hadees Qaaboos bin Abi Tibyaan sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai jisey unhoney apney walid sey aur un ke walid ne Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan riwayat ki hai. 2- is bab mein Saeed bin Zaid aur Harab bin Ubedullah Saqafi key dada sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm ka amal isi par hai ke nasrani jab Islam qubul kar ley to uski apni gardan ka jiziya maaf kar diya jaeyga, aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ke farman (ليس على المسلمين عشور) ''musalmanon par ushr nahin hai'' ka matlab bhi gardan ka jiziya hai, aur hadees mein bhi iki wazahat kar di gaee hai jaisa ke aap ney farmaya : ''ushr sirf Yahud aur Nasara par hai, musalmanon par koi ushr nahin.''"
635,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hum sey khitab kiya aur farmaya : ''aey giroh, aurton ki jamaat ! zakat do bhale apney zewrat hi sey kyon na do . kyonkey qiyamat key din jahannam walon main tum hi sab sey ziyada hogi.''"
636,"Abdullah bin Masood ki ehliya Zenab (Raziallahu Anha) key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah marvi hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye abu-Muaawia ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai. unhen apni hadees mein weham huwa hai padhi. unhoney kaha hai'' Amr bin al-Haaris sey riwayat hai wo Abdullah bin Masood ki biwi Zenab key bhatijey sey riwayat kar rahey hain'' aur sahih yun hai'' Zenab key bhatijey Amr bin Haris sey riwayat hai'' , 2- neez Amr bin Shuaib sey b-tareeq : « an Abeeh , an Jaddah, Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » riwayat hai ke aap ney zewrat mein zakat wajib qarar di hai padhi. is hadees ki sanad mein kalam hai, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ka is silsiley mein ikhtilaf hai. Sahaba kiram aur Tabe-een mein sey baaz ehle-ilm soney chaandi key zewrat mein zakat key qaail hain. Sufiyan Sory aur Abdullah bin Mubarak bhi yehi kehtey hain. aur baaz Sahaba kiram jin mein ibne-Umar , Aaisha , Jabir bin Abdullah aur Anas bin Malik (Raziallauh anhum) shamil hain, kehtey hain ke zewrat mein zakat nahin hai. baaz Tabe-een fuqaha sey bhi isi tarah marvi hai, aur yehi Malik bin Anas , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain."
637,"do aurten Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aain unkey haathon mein soney key do kangan they, to aap ney un sey farmaya : '' kya tum dono inki zakat ada karti ho?'' unhoney arz kya : nahin, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey farmaya : '' kya tum pasand karogi ke Allah tum dono ko aag key do kangan pahnaaey?'' unhoney arz kya : nahin, aap ney farmaya : '' to tum dono un ki zakat ada karo ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is hadees ko Musanna bin sabaah ney bhi Amr bin Shuaib sey isi tarah riwayat kya hai aur Musanna bin sabaah aur ibne-Lahia dono hadees mein zaeef gardaney jatey hain, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey is baab mein koi chiz sahih nahin hai."
638,"unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko likha , wo aap sey sabziyon ki zakat key barey mein poochh rahey they to aap ney farmaya : '' un mein koi zakat nahin hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ki sanad sahih nahin hai, 2- aur is baab mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey koi chiz sahih nahin hai, aur usey sirf Musa bin Talha sey riwayat kya jata hai aur unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan riwayat ki hai, 3- isi par ehle-ilm ka amal hai ke sabziyon mein zakat nahin hai, 4- Hasan, Imaara key betey hain, aur ye muhaddeseen key nazdik zaeef hain. Shoba waghera ney un ki tazeef ki hai, aur ibne-Mubarak ney unhen matrook qarar diya hai."
639,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jis fasal ki seenchai barish ya nehar key pani sey ki gaee ho, is mein zakat daswaan hissey hai, aur jiski seenchai dol sey khinch kar ki gaee ho to is mein zakat daswen hissey ka aadha yani beeswaan hissey padhi. hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Anas bin Malik , ibne-Umar aur Jabir sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 2- ye hadees bakeer bin Abdullah bin Ashajj, Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Yasar aur Basar bin Saeed sey bhi riwayat ki gaee hai, aur un sab ney isey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan riwayat ki hai, goya ye ziyada sahih hai, 3- aur is baab mein ibne-Umar ki hadees bhi sahih hai jisey unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai padhi. , 4- aur usi par beshtar fuqaha ka amal hai."
640,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ye tariqa jari farmaya ke jisey barish ya chashmey key pani ney sairab kya ho, ya Asri yani ratoobat wali zamin ho jisey pani deney ki zarurat na padti ho to is mein daswaan hissey zakat hai, aur jisey dol sey sairab kya jata ho is mein daswen ka aadha yani beeswaan hissa zakat hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
641,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney logon sey khitab kya to farmaya : '' jo kisi aisey yatim ka wali (sar parast) ho jis key paas kuch maal ho to wo usey tijarat mein laga dey, usey yunhi na chhod dey ke usey zakat kha ley. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sirf isi sanad sey marvi hai aur iski sanad mein kalam hai isliye ke Musanna bin Sabaah hadees mein zaeef gardaney jatey hain, 2- baaz logon ney ye hadees Amr bin Shuaib sey riwayat ki hai ke umr bin Khattab ney kaha : … aur aagey yehi hadees zikr ki, padhi. - Amr : Shuaib key betey hain, aur Shuaib Muhammad bin Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas key betey hain. aur Shuaib ney apney dada Abdullah bin Amr sey sama'at ki hai, Yahya bin Saeed ney Amr bin Shuaib ki hadees mein kalam kya hai. wo kehtey hain : ye hamarey nazdik zaeef hain, aur jisney unhen zaeef qarar diya hai sirf is wajeh sey zaeef kaha hai ke unhoney apney dada Abdullah bin Amr key sahifey sey hadees bayan ki hai. lekin aksar ehale- hadees ulama Amr bin Shuaib ki hadees sey daleel letey hain aur usey Sabit mantey hain jin mein Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya waghaira bhi shamil hain, 4- is bab mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai, Sahaba kiram mein sey kaee logon ki raey hai ke yatim key maal mein zakat hai, unhi mein umr , Ali , Aaisha , aur ibne-Umar hain. aur yehi Malik , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain, 5- aur ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat kehti hai ke yatim key maal mein zakat nahin hai. Sufiyan Sory aur Abdullah bin Mubarak ka yehi qol hai."
642,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''janwer ka zakham rayegaan hai padhi. yani maaf hai, kaan rayegaan hai aur kunwaan rayegaan hai padhi. aur dafeeney mein sey paanchwan hissa diya jaeyga''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Anas bin Malik , Abdullah bin Amr , Ubada bin Samit , Amr bin Auf Muzni aur Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
643,"Sehal bin abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) hamari majlis mein aaye to bayan kya ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam farmatey they : '' jab tum takhmina lagaao to takhmina key mutabiq lo aur eik tihai chhod diya karo, agar eik tihai na chhod sako to chothai chhod diya karo '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Aaisha , Itaab bin Usaid aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 2- takhmina laganey key silsiley mein aksar ehle-ilm ka amal Sehal bin abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees par hai aur Sehal bin abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees hi key mutabiq Ahmed aur Shafai bhi kehtey hain, takhmina lagana ye hai ke jab khajoor ya angoor key phal jinki zakat di jati hai pak jaeyn to sultan (intizamiya) eik takhmina laganey waley ko bhejey jo andaza laga kar bataey ke is mein kitna ghalla ya phal hoga aur takhmina lagana ye hai ke koi tajarba kaar aadmi dekh kar ye bataey ke us darkht sey itna itna angoor nikleyga, aur us sey itni itni khajoor nikleygi. phir wo usey jod kar dekhey ke kitna ushr ki miqdaar ko pahuncha , to un par wohi ushr muqarrar kar dey . aur phal key pakney tak in ko mohlat dey , phal todney key waqt apna ushr detey rahen . phir malikon ko ikhtiyar hoga ke baqiya sey jo chahen karen . baaz ehle-ilm ney takhmina laganey ki tashreeh isi tarah ki hai, aur yehi Malik Shafai Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain."
644,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam logon key paas eik aadmi bhejtey they jo unkey angooron aur doosrey phalon ka takhmina lagata tha. isi sanad sey hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney angoor ki zakat key barey mein farmaya : '' uska bhi takhmina lagaya jaeyga, jaisey khajoor ka lagaya jata hai, phir kishmish ho janey key baad uski zakat nikali jaeygi jaisey khajoor ki zakat tamr ho janey key baad nikali jati hai. ( yani jab khushk ho jaeyn ( '' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- ibne-Juraij ney ye hadees b-tareeq : « ibne-Shahab, an Urwah, an Aaisha» riwayat ki hai, padhi. - mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is hadees key barey mein puchha : to unhoney kaha : ibne-Juraij ki hadees mehfooz nahin hai aur ibn Musaiyab ki hadees jisey unhoney itaab bin Usaid sey riwayat ki hai ziyada Sabit aur ziyada sahih hai) bas sirf sanad ke aitibar sey , warna zaeef ye bhi hai) ."
645,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : '' sahih dhang sey sadqa wasul karney wala , Allah ki raah mein ladney waley ghaazi ki tarah hai, jab tak ke wo apney ghar lot na aaye ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Raafey bin khadij ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- aur Yazeed bin ayaaz muhaddeseen key nazdik zaeef hain, 3- Muhammad bin Is-haq ki ye hadees sab sey ziyada sahih hai."
646,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' zakat wasul karney mein zulm o ziyadti karney wala zakat na deney waley ki tarah hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein ibne-Umar, Umme-Salma aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 2- Anas ki hadees is sanad sey gharib hai, 3- Ahmed bin Hanbal ney Saad bin Sanan key silsiley mein kalam kya hai. isi tarah Les bin Saad bhi kehtey hain. wo bhi «an Yazid bin Habib, an Saad bin Sanaan, an Anas bin maalik» kehtey hain, aur Amr bin Haris aur ibne-Lahiaa «an Yazid bin Habib, an Sanan bin Saad, an Anas bin maalik» kehtey hain, 4- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna ke sahih '' Sanan bin Saad'' hai, 5- aur zakat wasul karney mein ziyadti karney wala zakat na deney waley ki tarah hai ka matlab ye hai ke ziyadti karney waley par wohi gunah hai jo na deney waley par hai."
647,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab zakat wasul karney wala tumharey paas aaye to wo tum sey razi aur khush ho kar hi juda ho''.
648,"Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah marvi hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Dawud ki Shaaby sey riwayat ki hui hadees Majaalid ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai, Majaalid ko baaz ehle-ilm ney zaeef gardana hai wo kasirul-ghalat hain yani un sey b-kasrat ghaltiyaan hoti hain."
649,"hamarey paas Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka musaddiq ( zakat wasul karney wala ( aaya aur usney zakat hamarey maaldaaron sey li aur usey hamarey fuqara ko dey diya. main us waqt eik yatim ladka tha, to usney mujhey bhi is mein sey eik oontni di . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Juhaifa ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai,"
650,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo logon sey sawal karey aur uskey paas itna maal ho ke usey sawal karney sey be-niaz kar dey to wo qiyamat key din is tarah aayega ke uska sawal karna uskey chehrey par kharaash hogi, arz kya gaya : Allah key Rasool! kitney maal sey wo sawal karney sey be-niaz ho jata hai? aap ney farmaya : '' pachas dirham ya uski qeemat key b-qadr soney sey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Masood ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- Shoba ney isi hadees ki wajeh sey Hakim bin Juber par kalam kya hai."
651,"ye hadees isi sanad sey riwayat ki hai. jab Sufiyan ney ye hadees riwayat ki to un sey Shoba key shagrid Abdullah bin Usman ney kaha : kaash! Hakim key ilawa kisi aur ney is hadees ko bayan kya hota , to Sufiyan ney un sey puchha padhi. : kya baat hai ke Shoba Hakim sey hadees riwayat nahin kartey ? unhoney kaha : haan , wo nahin kartey . to Sufiyan ney kaha : mainey usey Zubeda ko Muhammad bin Abdur-Rehman bin Yazid sey riwayat kartey suna hai, aur usi par hamarey baaz as-haab ka amal hai aur yehi Sufiyan Sory, Abdullah bin Mubarak, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain, un logon ka kehna hai ke jab aadmi key paas pachas dirham hon to uskey liye zakat jayez nahin۔ aur baaz ehle-ilm Hakim bin Juber ki hadees ki taraf nahin gaey hain balke unhoney is mein mazeed gunjaaish rakhi hai, wo kehtey hain ke jab kisi key paas pachas dirham ya us sey ziyada hon aur wo zaruratmand ho to us ko zakat leney ka haq hai, ehale-fiq'h o ehale-hadees mein sey Shafai waghera ka yehi qol hai."
652,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kisi maaldaar key liye maangna jayez nahin aur na kisi taqatwar aur sahih Salim shakhs key liye maangna jayez hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin Amr ki hadees Hasan hai, 2- aur Shoba ney bhi ye hadees isi sanad sey Saad bin Ibrahim sey riwayat ki hai, lekin unhoney usey marfoo nahin kya hai, padhi. 3- is bab mein abu-Huraira, Habshi bin Junada aur Qabisa bin Makhariq (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 4- aur is hadees key ilawa mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi hai ke '' kisi maaldaar key liye maangna jayez nahin aur na kisi hatey katey key liye maangna jayez hai'' aur jab aadmi taqatwar o tawana ho lekin mohtaj ho aur uskey paas kuch na ho aur usey sadqa diya jaey to ehle-ilm key nazdik us deney waley ki zakat ada ho jaeygi۔ baaz ehle-ilm ney is hadees ki tojeeh ye ki hai ke «la تحل له الصدقة » ka matlab hai ke uskey liye maangna durust nahin hai."
653,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko hajjatul-wadaa mein farmatey suna aap Arfa mein khadey they, aap key paas eik ea'rab aaya aur aap ki chadar ka kinaara pakad kar aap sey manga , aap ney isey diya aur wo chala gaya, us waqt maangna haram huwa , to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kisi maaldaar key liye maangna jayez nahin na kisi hatey katey sahih Salim aadmi key liye siwaye jaan lewa faqr waley key aur kisi bhaari tawaan mein dabey shakhs key. aur jo logon sey isliye maangey ke uskey zariey sey apna maal badhaey to ye maal qiyamat key din uskey chehrey par kharaash hoga . aur wo jahannam ka eik garm pathar hoga jisey wo kha raha hoga, to jo chahey usey kam kar ley aur jo chahey ziyada kar ley.''"
654,abdur-Raheem bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) sey isi tarah marvi hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is sanad sey ye hadees gharib hai.
655,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney main eik shakhs padhi. key phalon mein jo usney khareedey they, kisi aafat ki wajeh sey jo usey laahiq hui nuqsan ho gaya aur is par qarz ziyada ho gaya, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' usey sadqa do '' chunanche logon ney isey sadqa diya, magar wo uskey qarz ki miqdaar ko na pahuncha, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney uskey qarz khaahon sey farmaya : '' jitna mil raha hai ley lo , uskey ilawa tumharey liye kuch nahin ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Saeed ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha , juweriya aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
656,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas jab koi chiz laee jati to aap poochhtey : '' sadqa hai ya hadiya ? '' agar log kehtey ke sadqa hai to aap nahin khatey aur agar kehtey ke hadiya hai to kha letey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Behaz bin Hakim ki ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Salman , Abu-Hurera , Anas , Hasan bin Ali , abu-Umera ( Moraf bin Wasil key dada hain unka naam rasheed bin Malik hai) , Memun (ya Mehran ( , ibne-Abbas , Abdullah bin Amr , abu-Raafey aur Abdur-Rehman bin Alqama (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- neez ye hadees Abdur-Rehman bin Alqama , sey bhi marvi hai unhoney usey Abdur-Rehman bin abi Aqeel sey aur Abdur-Rehman ney Nabi Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai."
657,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney bani makhzoom key eik shakhs ko sadqa ki wasuli par bheja to usney abu-Raafey sey kaha : tum merey sath chalo taake tum bhi is mein sey hissa paa sako, magar unhoney kaha : nahin, yahan tak ke main ja kar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey poochh lun , chunanche unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas ja kar puchha to aap ney farmaya : '' hamarey liye sadqa halal nahin, aur qom key mawaali bhi qom hi mein sey hain'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- abu-Raafey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key Mola hain, unka naam Aslam hai aur ibne-Abi Raafey ka naam Ubedullah bin abi Raafey hai, wo Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) key munshi they."
658,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum mein sey koi roza iftaar karey to khajoor sey iftaar karey , kyonkey is mein barkat hai, agar khajoor muyassar na ho to pani sey iftaar karey wo nihayat pakizah chiz hai'' , neez farmaya : '' miskeen par sadqa , sirf sadqa hai aur rishtedaar par sadqey mein do bhalaiyan hain, ye sadqa bhi hai aur sila rehmi bhi ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Salman bin Aamir ki hadees Hasan hai, 2- Sufiyan Sory ney bhi Aasim sey b-tareeq : « Hafsa binte-Sereen, an Rubab, an Salman bin Aamir , an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » isi hadees ki tarah riwayat ki hai, 3- neez Shoba ney b-tareeq : « Aasim , an Hafsa, an Salman bin Aamir » riwayat ki hai aur is mein unhoney Rubab ka zikr nahin kya hai, 4- Sufiyan Sory aur ibn Uena ki hadees padhi. ziyada sahih hai, 5- isi tarah ibne-Aun aur Hisham bin Hassan ney bhi b-tareeq : «Hafsa, an Rubab, an Salman bin Aamir » riwayat ki hai, 6- is bab mein Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki ehliya Zenab , Jabir aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
659,"mainey zakat key barey mein puchha , ya Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey zakat key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : '' maal mein zakat key ilawa bhi kuch haq hai padhi. '' phir aap ney Sura Baqra ki ye aayat tilawat farmaai : « ليس البر أن تولوا وجوهكم » '' neki ye nahin hai ke tum apney chehrey pher lo '' padhi. puri aayat"
660,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' maal mein zakat key ilawa bhi huquq hain ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ki sanad koi khas nahin hai padhi. , 2- abu-Hamza Memun al-Aur ko zaeef gardana jata hai, 3- bayan aur Ismail bin Salim ney ye hadees Shaaby sey riwayat ki hai aur usey Shaaby hi ka qol qarar diya hai aur yehi ziyada sahih hai."
661,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney bhi kisi pakizah chiz ka sadqa kya aur Allah pakizah chiz hi qubul karta hai padhi. to Rehman usey apney daain haath sey leta hai padhi. agar-che wo eik khajoor hi ho, ye maal sadqa Rehman ki hatheli mein badhta rehta hai, yahan tak ke wo pahad sey bada ho jata hai, jaisey ke tum mein sey eik apney ghodey key bachey ya gaey key bachey ko paaltaa hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ummul-momenin Aaisha , Adi bin Hatim , Anas , Abdullah bin abi Aufi , Harisa bin Wahab , Abdur-Rehman bin Auf aur Barida (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
662,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah sadqa qubul karta hai aur usey apney daain haath sey leta hai aur usey paalta hai jaisey tum mein sey koi apney ghodey key bachdey ko paaltaa hai yahan tak ke luqma Uhad pahad key misl ho jata hai. uski tasdeeq Allah ki kitab ( Quran ( sey hoti hai, Allah Taala farmata hai «ألم يعلموا أن الله هو يقبل التوبة an عباده ويأخذ الصدقات» '' kya unhen nahin malum ke Allah hi hai jo apney bandon ki tauba qubul karta hai aur sadqaat leta hai'' aur  ( يمحق الله الربا ويربي الصدقات‏ » '' Allah sood ko mitata hai aur sadqaat ko badhata hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- neez Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey marvi hai ke unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm mein sey bahut sey logon ney is hadees key barey mein aur is jaisi sifaat ki dusri riwayaat key barey mein aur Bari Taala key har raat aasmane-duniya par utarney key barey mein kaha hai ke ''is silsiley ki riwayaat Sabit hain, un par eman laya jaey, un mein kisi qism ka weham na kya jaeyga, aur na uski keyfiyat poochhi jaey, aur isi tarah Malik, Sufiyan bin Uena aur Abdullah bin Mubarak sey marvi hai, un logon ney un ahadees key barey mein kaha hai ke in hadison ko bila kaifiyat jari karo padhi. isi tarah ka qol ehale-sunnat wal-jamaat key ehle-ilm ka hai, albatta Jehmiya ney un riwayaat ka inkar kya hai, wo kehtey hain ke un sey tashbih lazim aati hai. Allah Taala ney apni kitab key kaee maqamat par '' haath , kaan , aankh '' ka zikr kya hai. Jehmiya ney un aayaat ki taawil ki hai aur un ki aisi tashreeh ki hai jo ehle-ilm ki tafseer key khilaf hai, wo kehtey hain ke Allah ney Adam ko apney haath sey paida nahin kya, darasal haath key maana yahan quwat key hain. Is-haq bin Ibrahim bin Raahviya kehtey hain : tashbih to tab hogi jab koi kahey : «يد كيد أو مثل يد» ya « سمع كسمع أو مثل سمع» '' yani Allah ka haath hamarey haath ki tarah hai, ya hamarey haath key maanind hai, uska kaan hamarey kaan ki tarah hai ya hamarey kaan key maanind hai'' to ye tashbeeh hui. (na ke sirf ye kehna ke Allah ka haath hai, us sey tashbih lazim nahin aati (aur jab koi kahey jaisey Allah ney kaha hai ke uskey haath kaan aur aankh hai aur ye na kahey ke wo kaisey hain aur na ye kahey ke falan key kaan ki maanind ya falan key kaan ki tarah hai to ye tashbih nahin hui, ye aisey hi hai jaisey Allah Taala ney apni kitab mein farmaya : « ليس كمثله شيئ وهو السميع البصير » '' us jaisi koi chiz nahin hai aur wo samee hai baseer hai ''."
663,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha gaya : Ramzan key baad kon sey rozey afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : ''Shoban key rozey jo Ramzan ki tazeem key liye hon'', puchha gaya : kon sa sadqa afzal hai? farmaya : '' Ramzan mein sadqa karna ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- Sadqa bin Musa muhaddeseen key nazdik ziyada qawi Raavi nahin hain."
664,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' sadqa rab key ghussey ko bujha deta hai aur buri maut sey bachata hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai.
665,"Umme Bujed hawaa (Raziallahu Anha) ( jo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey baiat karney waaliyon mein sey hain ( sey riwayat hai ke unhoney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! miskeen merey darwazey par khada hota hai aur usey deney key liye merey paas koi chiz nahin hoti .) to main kya karun ? ( Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey farmaya : '' agar usey deney key liye tumhen koi jali hui khir hi miley to wohi uskey haath mein dey do''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Umme Bujed (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali, Husein bin Ali, Abu-Hurera aur abu-Umama (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
666,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Hunain key roz mujhey diya, aap mujhey (fatah Makka sey qabl) tamam makhluq mein sab sey ziyada mabghooz they, aur barabar aap mujhey detey rahey yahan tak ke aap mujhey makhluq mein sab sey ziyada mehbub ho gaey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Hasan bin Ali ney mujh sey is hadees ya us jaisi chiz ko muzaakra mein bayan kya, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- Safwan ki hadees Maamar waghera ney Zohri sey aur Zohri ney Saeed bin Musaiyab sey riwayat ki hai jis mein (عن صفوان بن أمية) key bajaey ( أن صفوان بن أمية قال أعطاني رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم) hai goya ye hadees Yunus bin Yazeed ki hadees sey ziyada sahih aur اشبہ hai, ye ( عن سعيد بن مسيب أن صفوان ) key bajaey ( عن سعيد بن مسيب أن صفوان ) hi hai padhi. , 4- jinka dil rijhana aur jinko qarib lana maqsud ho unhen deney key silsiley mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai, aksar ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke unhen na diya jaey. unka kehna hai ke ye Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney key chand log they jinki aap taaleefe-qalb farma rahey they yahan tak ke wo Islam ley aaye lekin ab is tarah har kisi ko zakat ka maal dena jayez nahin hai, Sufiyan Sory, ehle-koofa waghera isi key qaail hain, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain aur baaz kehtey hain ke agar koi aaj bhi un logon jaisi haalat mein ho aur Imam Islam key liye uski taaleef qalb zaruri samjhey aur usey kuch dey to ye jayez hai, ye Shafai ka qol hai."
667,"main Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas betha huwa tha, itney main eik aurat ney aap key paas aa kar kaha : Allah key Rasool ! mainey apni maa ko eik laundi sadqey mein di thi, ab wo mar gaeen ( to us laundi ka kya hoga?) aap ney farmaya : ''tumhen sawab bhi mil gaya aur meeras ney isey tumhen lota bhi diya ''. usney puchha : Allah key Rasool! meri maa par eik maah key rozey farz they, kya main un ki taraf sey rozey rakh lun? aap ney farmaya : ''to unki taraf sey roza rakh ley'', usney puchha : Allah key Rasool! unhoney kabhi Haj nahin kya, kya main un ki taraf sey Haj kar lun ? aap ney farmaya : '' haan , un ki taraf sey Haj kar ley ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Barida (Raziallahu anhu) ki ye hadees sirf isi tareeq sey jaani jati hai. 3- aksar ehle-ilm ka amal usi par hai ke aadmi jab koi sadqa karey phir wo uska waris ho jaey to uskey liye wo jayez hai, 4- aur baaz kehtey hain : sadqa to usney Allah ki khatir kya tha lihaza jab uska waris ho jaey to lazim hai ke phir usey usi key raastey mein sarf kar dey ( ye ziyada afzal hai) ."
668,"unhoney kisi ko eik ghoda Allah ki raah mein diya, phir dekha ke wo ghoda becha ja raha hai to usey khareedna chaha, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''apna sadqa wapis na lo''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai."
669,"eik shakhs ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! meri walida faut ho chuki hain, agar main un ki taraf sey sadqa karun to kya ye unkey liye mufeed hoga? aap ney farmaya : '' haan '' , usney arz kya : mera eik baagh hai, aap gawah rahiye ke mainey usey walida ki taraf sey sadqey mein dey diya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- baaz logon ney ye hadees b-tareeq « an Amr bin Dinar an Ikrima an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » mursalan riwayat ki hai, 3- aur yehi ehle-ilm bhi kehtey hain ke koi chiz aisi nahin hai jo maiyat ko pahunchti ho siwaye sadqa aur dua key padhi. , 4- « إن لي مخرفا » mein « مخرفاً » sey murad baagh hai."
670,"mainey hajjatul-wadaa key saal Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko apney khutbey mein farmatey suna : ''aurat apney shohar key ghar sey uski ijazat key baghair kuch kharch na kerey'' , arz kya gaya : Allah key Rasool ! aur khana bhi nahin ? . aap ney farmaya : '' ye hamarey maalon mein sab sey afzal maal hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Saad bin abi Waqas , Asma bint abi Bakr , Abu-Hurera , Abdullah bin Amr aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
671,"ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab aurat apney shohar key ghar sey sadqa karey to usey uska ajr milta hai aur itna hi ajr uskey shohar ko bhi, aur khazaanchi ko bhi, aur un mein kisi ka ajr doosrey key ajr ki wajeh sey kam nahin kya jata. shohar ko uskey kamaaney ka ajr milta hai aur aurat ko uskey kharch karney ka''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
672,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab aurat apney shohar key ghar sey khush dili key sath baghair fasad ki niyat key koi chiz dey to usey mard key sawab key barabar sawab milega. usey apni nek-niyati ka sawab milega aur khaazin ko bhi isi tarah sawab milega''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye Amr bin Murra ki hadees sey jisey unhoney abu-Waeil sey riwayat ki hai, ziyada sahih hai, Amr bin Murra apni riwayat mein Masruq key wastey ka zikr nahin kartey hain."
673,"hum log jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hamarey darmiyan mojud they, sadqa fitr padhi. main eik saa gehun ya eik saa jo, ya eik saa khajoor ya eik saa kishmish ya eik saa paneer nikaltey they. to hum isi tarah barabar sadqa fitr nikaltey rahey yahan tak ke Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) Madina aaye, to unhoney logon sey khitab kya, us khitab mein ye baat bhi thi ke main Sham key do mudd gehun ko eik saa khajoor key barabar samajhta hun, to logon ney usi ko ikhtiyar kar liya yani log do mudd aadha saa gehun deney lagey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai unka khayal hai ke har chiz main eik saa hai, yehi Shafai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke har chiz main eik saa hai siwaye gehun key, is mein aadha saa kafi hai, 4- yehi Sufiyan Sory aur ibne-Mubarak ka bhi qol hai. aur ehle-koofa ki bhi raey hai ke gehun mein nisf saa hi hai."
674,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik shakhs ko Makka ki galiyon mein manadi karney key liye bheja ke '' suno ! sadqa fitr har musalman mard ho ya aurat , azad ho ya ghulam , chhota ho ya bada , gehun sey do mudd aur gehun key ilawa doosrey ghallon sey eik saa wajib hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 3- umr bin Harun ney ye hadees ibne-Jurej sey riwayat ki, aur kaha : « Abbas bin Meena an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam» phir aagey is hadees ka kuch hissa zikr kya."
675,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney sadqa fitr mard , aurat , azad aur ghulam par , eik saa khajoor , ya eik saa jo farz kya, Raavi kehtey hain : phir logon ney aadha saa gehun ko uskey barabar kar liya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Saeed , ibne-Abbas , Haris bin Abdur-Rehman bin abi zubab key dada ( yani abu-Zubab ( , Solba bin abi Saeer aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
676,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Ramzan ka sadqa fitr eik saa khajoor ya eik saa jo musalmanon mein sey har azad aur ghulam , mard aur aurat par farz kya hai padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Malik ney bhi b-tareeq : ( نافع an ابن عمر an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم ) Ayub ki hadees ki tarah riwayat ki hai albatta us mein (من المسلمين) ka izafa hai. 3- aur deegar kaee logon ney Nafey sey riwayat ki hai, us mein (من المسلمين) ka zikr nahin hai, 4- ehle-ilm ka is silsiley mein ikhtilaf hai baaz kehtey hain ke jab aadmi key paas ghair Muslim ghulam hun to wo unka sadqa fitr ada nahin kerega. yehi Malik , Shafai aur Ahmed ka qol hai. aur baaz kehtey hain ke wo ghulamon ka sadqa fitr ada kerega chahey wo ghair Muslim hi kyon na hon, ye Sory, ibne-Mubarak aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai."
677,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam eidul-Fitr key din namaz key liye janey sey pehley sadqa fitr nikalney ka hukm detey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- aur ehle-ilm usi ko mustahab samajhtey hain ke aadmi sadqa fitr namaz key liye janey sey pehley nikal dey."
678,Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey apni zakat waqt sey pehley deney key barey mein puchha to aap ney unhen uski ijazat di.
679,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : '' hum Abbas sey us saal ki zakat guzishta saal hi ley chukey hain ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, 2- Israel ki pehley zakat nikalney wali hadees ko jisey unhoney hujjaaj bin Dinar sey riwayat ki hai hum sirf usi tareeq sey jantey hain, 3- Ismail bin Zakariya ki hadees jisey unhoney Hujjaaj sey riwayat ki hai merey nazdik Israel ki hadees sey jisey unhoney hujjaaj bin Dinar sey riwayat ki hai ziyada sahih hai, 4- neez ye hadees Hakam bin Uteba sey bhi marvi hai unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan riwayat ki hai, 5- ehle-ilm ka waqt sey pehley peshgi zakat deney mein ikhtilaf hai, ehle-ilm mein sey eik jamaat ki raey hai ke usey peshgi ada na kerey. Sufiyan Sory usi key qaail hain, wo kehtey hain : ke merey nazdik ziyada pasandida yehi hai ke usey peshgi ada na kerey. aur aksar ehle-ilm ka kehna hai ke agar waqt sey pehley peshgi ada kar dey to jayez hai. Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya usi key qaail hain۔"
680,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : ''tum mein sey koi shakhs subh sawerey jaey aur lakdiyon ka gatthar apni peeth par rakh kar laye aur is mein sey (yani uski qeemat mein sey) sadqa karey aur is tarah logon sey be niaz rahey (yani un sey na maangey) uskey liye is baat sey behtar hai ke wo kisi sey maangey, wo usey dey ya na dey padhi. kyonkey ooper wala haath nichey waley haath sey afzal hai, aur pehley usey do jiski tum khud kafalat kartey ho''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- wo bayan ki hadees sey jisey unhoney Qais sey riwayat ki hai gharib jaani jati hai, padhi. 3- is bab mein Hakim bin Hizam, abu Saeed Khudri, Zuber bin Awam, Atiya Sadi, Abdullah bin Masood , Masood bin Amr, ibne-Abbas 'Soban' Ziyad bin Haris Sadaai, Anas, Habshi bin Junada, Qabisa bin Makhariq, Samra aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
681,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''maangna eik zakham hai jis sey aadmi apna chehra zakhmi kar leta hai, siwaye iskey ke aadmi haakim sey maangey padhi. ya kisi aisey kaam key liye maangey jo zaruri aur naaguzeer ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
